author: YT C
text:
To give fellow overseas bros context
Tamaki: help me...... help me........
Rushia: that's not possible, Tamaki-kun


even more context of what's happening here: Rushia set up a fall trap, luring a zombie, get killed by the zombie (zombie-kun got her enchanted diamond sword, F for sword-kun), then name the zombie with nametag "たまきくん" (romanized: Tamaki kun) then lock the zombie in the trap hole, that's why Tamaki says "help me...... help me......"

author: Nexcell Pride
text:
A great streaming, with more action and adventure... And sometimes fun facts, but after all, so epic :_ちょうちょ: :_るんるん:

Rushia's character again fell to slime trap, but now she was lucky, because the fixing made by Pekora-san, and also, Rushia learnt to use the elevator.

Also an exchange with Flare-san, A mystery box... And many disasters like Subaru's trap being activated many times and Rushia thinking about Creepers explosions... At least Rushia Provisioned Trinitrotoluene to Subaru-san for repair the surprise trap.
But the mission was the Halloween Cabin... And also a dangerous trap with zombies.

And Fubuki-san giving her a diamond unit meanwhile harvesting...

Supaachaato Orei Time was about 45 minutes today. Too many action in this stream. :_ハート: and more "chuu" :_きゅん:
